Cell[TextData[{
 "The Mandelbrot set became a rite of passage for anyone programming \
mathematical images. For me, I was making images on a Mac Plus, and sent some \
of them out in a zine I was running at the time. As a result, ",
 ButtonBox["Piers Anthony ",
  BaseStyle->"Hyperlink",
  ButtonData->{
    URL["http://www.hipiers.com/"], None},
  ButtonNote->"http://www.hipiers.com/"],
 "asked me to help get fractal images and facts for his Mode series. In the \
course of this, Piers and I asked for and received permission to use the \
Mandelbrot set from Beno\[IHat]t himself. \"You probably don't need my \
permission, but I'm happy to grant it to you.\""
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.4964199536131053`*^9, 3.4964199865981054`*^9}, {
   3.4964204438495784`*^9, 3.4964205166998625`*^9}, {3.4964205475499477`*^9, 
