Cell[TextData[{
 "Seems like just a few days ago that I wrote blog posts with ",
 ButtonBox["fractal mazes",
  BaseStyle->"Hyperlink",
  ButtonData->{
    URL["http://blog.wolfram.com/2010/09/"], None},
  ButtonNote->"http://blog.wolfram.com/2010/09/"],
 " and ",
 ButtonBox["cool points on the complex plane",
  BaseStyle->"Hyperlink",
  ButtonData->{
    URL["http://blog.wolfram.com/2010/08/06/nine-cool-points-on-the-complex-\
plane/"], None},
  ButtonNote->
   "http://blog.wolfram.com/2010/08/06/nine-cool-points-on-the-complex-plane/\
"],
 ". For years, I've never failed to be amazed by the beauty of these worlds. \
They were a surprise for Beno\[IHat]t himself\[LongDash]he thought some of \
his initial printouts might be an error. To get a sense of the vastness, a \
great video is \"",
 ButtonBox["Trip to e214",
  BaseStyle->"Hyperlink",
  ButtonData->{
    URL["http://vimeo.com/1908224"], None},
  ButtonNote->"http://vimeo.com/1908224"],
 "\". Magnifying an electron to the size of the universe needs a \
magnification of ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SuperscriptBox["10", "42"], TraditionalForm]]],
 ". This video magnifies the target mandelbulb ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SuperscriptBox["10", "214"], TraditionalForm]]],
 " times."
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.4964226252427006`*^9, 3.496422631097286*^9}, {
   3.4964228826444383`*^9, 3.496422898340008*^9}, {3.496423159280099*^9, 
   3.4964233391160808`*^9}, {3.4964234133715057`*^9, 3.496423483549523*^9}, {
   3.4964235202231894`*^9, 3.496423526367804*^9}, {3.4964237564168067`*^9, 
   3.4964238196221266`*^9}, 3.496424806603815*^9, {3.496426604648608*^9, 
   3.4964266668845763`*^9}, {3.4964924786364274`*^9, 3.4964925222801247`*^9}}],

